- Automate the starting of the gateway (sh startGateway etc)
- Automate the startiung of the web server (nginx etc)
- Research how to get the website to show up in a browser like a normal website (on customer PC be able to open firefox and visit our website)
- Decide what file upload system we are going to use (SFTP, etc). 
- Make sure you can't ping internal servers from the customer PC.
- Do a BCP/BIA/RA/IT DR. 
